<reference id="api_stopaudiorecording">
    <title><ph keyref="stopAudioRecording"/></title>
    <shortdesc id="short"><ph id="shortdesc">停止客户端录音。</ph></shortdesc>
    <prolog>
        <metadata>
   <keywords>
       <indexterm keyref="stopAudioRecording" />
   </keywords>
        </metadata>
    </prolog>
    <refbody><section id="prototype">
        
        <p conref="../conref/conref_rtc_api.dita#apidef/stopAudioRecording"/>
        </section>
        <section id="detailed_desc">
   
   <p>停止录音。该接口需要在 <xref keyref="leaveChannel"/> 之前调用，不然会在调用 <apiname keyref="leaveChannel"/> 时自动停止。</p>
        </section>
        <section id="return_values">
   <title>返回值</title>
   <ul>
       <li>0: 方法调用成功</li>
       <li>&lt; 0: 方法调用失败</li>
   </ul>
        </section></refbody>
</reference>
